	<img src="//images.nationalgeographic.com/wpf/media-live/photos/000/845/cache/ebola-vaccine-create-01_84577_600x450.jpg"  width="600" height="414" alt="A photo of a professor holding a vial of experimental Ebola vaccine." />	


                        

                        
